<p>There is a rumour going about to night that the 2nd Division have advanced nearly a mile, I would not be surprised for we cracked the nut that was so hard</p>
<p>Jock Mackie, Howard, &amp; I went for a little stroll round the pretty little village this evening, &amp; made a few purchases.</p>
<p>We are having lovely weather at the present time nice &amp; hot.</p>
<p>30th.   Fairly liberal scale of rations this morning, we live pretty well take it all round, though at times we have to do a starve</p>
